rows.label: qst200711_msg0001
rows.name:
N-no... To think Maumau
would lose twice-mau...

rows.label: qst200711_msg0002
rows.name:
You've won twice now, so that
should settle it, right?

rows.label: qst200711_msg0003
rows.name: That's not true-mau!

rows.label: qst200711_msg0004
rows.name:
It's standard for a duel to
be three rounds-mau! There's
still one more left-mau!

rows.label: qst200711_msg0005
rows.name: But we've already won two out of three?

rows.label: qst200711_msg0006
rows.name:
All's well that ends
well-mau! The one who wins
last is the winner-mau!

rows.label: qst200711_msg0007
rows.name: He's starting to talk nonsense...

rows.label: qst200711_msg0022
rows.name:
Idaten is fed up-ppo! The
high-risk Maumau mentioned
wasn't delicious at all-ppo...

rows.label: qst200711_msg0023
rows.name:
Don't say that-mau... But you can
look forward to the last one-mau!

rows.label: qst200711_msg0008
rows.name:
A content worthy of the
final battle... It is...

rows.label: qst200711_msg0009
rows.name: A mushroom-mau!

rows.label: qst200711_msg0010
rows.name: A mushroom-ppo!?

rows.label: qst200711_msg0011
rows.name: Yes, a mushroom-mau!

rows.label: qst200711_msg0012
rows.name:
The phantom mushroom that was on the
mushroom ship that sank 100 years ago...
Its name is the Mashimashidake-mau!

rows.label: qst200711_msg0021
rows.name:
There's a rumor that the Ignas at the
Varrac main camp in Temperantia are
worshipping it as a treasure-mau.

rows.label: qst200711_msg0013
rows.name: Let's compete to steal this-mau!

rows.label: qst200711_msg0014
rows.name:
A 100-year-old mushroom...
Sounds delicious-ppo!

rows.label: qst200711_msg0015
rows.name:
After 100 years, even a
phantom mushroom would
probably be rotten, mo...

rows.label: qst200711_msg0016
rows.name:
Tora doesn't get it-ppo! Slightly
rotten is the most delicious-ppo!

rows.label: qst200711_msg0017
rows.name: I accept that challenge-ppo!

rows.label: qst200711_msg0018
rows.name:
This time, Maumau will win-mau! And I
will reclaim the hearts of the lovely
Nopon that Idaten stole from me-mau!

rows.label: qst200711_msg0019
rows.name: Let's hurry-ppo!

rows.label: qst200711_msg0020
rows.name:
I can't let the
Mashimashidake get away-ppo!
